column2: "Although the Guardian's endeavors had released the country from [Double]'s grasp, the Demons had still not yet vanished from Es-Ars."
"Queen Harriet of Cuent led her armies in numerous battles along the border in order to halt their advance."
"The Guardian, too, fought on the frontlines. However, a twinge of anxiety had been eating away at their thoughts."
"All traces of Dark Falz [Double] have finally vanished... We're done here, at last."
"The root of all this evil still remains"
"...You're right. Both [Profound Darkness] and Elmir are still out there somewhere."
"Elmir especially. He keeps showing up in all the wrong places. Where could he be...?"
"What...is that...?! Isn't that around where Harriet's camp was set up?!"
